ZH: 我每天搭乘公共汽车上班。
EN: I take the bus to work every day.

ZH: 他们搭乘飞机去旅行。
EN: They travel by plane.

ZH: 我们将搭乘高铁去北京。
EN: We will take the high-speed train to Beijing.

ZH: 昨天我搭乘出租车回家。
EN: Yesterday, I took a taxi home.

ZH: 他选择搭乘地铁来参加会议。
EN: He chose to take the subway to attend the meeting.

ZH: 我们明天准备搭乘轮船去海岛度假。
EN: We are planning to take a cruise to the island for a vacation tomorrow.

ZH: 妈妈要搭乘火车去看望奶奶。
EN: Mom is going to take the train to visit Grandma.

ZH: 我们需要提前预订机票才能搭乘飞机。
EN: We need to book the flight tickets in advance to board the plane.

ZH: 他们将搭乘游轮环游世界。
EN: They will embark on a world tour by cruise ship.

ZH: 我们在机场等待搭乘下一班航班。
EN: We are waiting at the airport to board the next flight.

ZH: 出差期间，她需要搭乘长途汽车。
EN: During her business trip, she needs to take the long-distance bus.

ZH: 我打算搭乘火车回家度假。
EN: I plan to take the train home for vacation.

ZH: 他们决定搭乘电车去购物中心。
EN: They decided to take the tram to the shopping mall.

ZH: 我每天早上都搭乘地铁上班。
EN: I take the subway to work every morning.

ZH: 她比较喜欢搭乘轮船旅行。
EN: She prefers traveling by boat.

ZH: 他们将在明天早上六点搭乘巴士去机场。
EN: They will take the bus to the airport at 6 o'clock tomorrow morning.

ZH: 我在网上预订了一辆出租车来搭乘。
EN: I booked a taxi online for pick-up.

ZH: 我们可以搭乘观光巴士游览城市。
EN: We can take the sightseeing bus to tour the city.

ZH: 为了方便出行，我建议你搭乘地铁。
EN: To facilitate your travel, I suggest you take the subway.

ZH: 我们需要提前预定车票才能搭乘火车。
EN: We need to book train tickets in advance to board the train.
